data.description: PRICED TO SELL!  COBBLESTONE COMMUNITY, LOW HOA, EASY COMMUTE TO MIAMI USING 1-75  This COURTYARD TOWNHOME is a FULL 3/3 with *ONE BEDROOM AND BATHROOM DOWNSTAIRS*, 2 CAR GARAGE WITH STORAGE, LOFT/OFFICE. Some features include a quartz island with open storage, 2 wine coolers, Nest & Ring security, full size stackable washer and dryer, wood custom closets in all bedrooms, private courtyard as well as a BBQ area, balcony in second bedroom, porcelain wood plank floors and laminate wood. Main bathroom has a free-standing soaking bathtub as well as a walk-in shower and water closet.   Residents only entrance on Pembroke Rd. easy 1-75 access for commuting, tons of shopping and restaurants nearby, 24/7 manned gate plus roaming security, basic cable and security system.
